CommonEvent 1
Name = "Go Vs Hu city"

  Page 0
    Comment(["<always update>"])
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["Join the battle?"])
    ShowChoices([["Yes, with the humans!", "Of course, with the golem!", "No"], 3])
    When([0, "Yes, with the humans!"])
      ControlSwitches([634, 634, 0])
      ControlSwitches([588, 588, 0])
      CallCommonEvent([49])

      ControlSwitches([636, 636, 0])
      ControlSwitches([587, 587, 0])
      CallCommonEvent([49])
      Empty([])

    When([2, "No"])
      Empty([])

    ChoicesEnd([])
    Empty([])

CommonEvent 8
Name = "Bandit encounter"

  Page 0
    Comment([":update:"])
    ControlVariables([23, 23, 0, 2, 1, 30])
    Wait([600])
    ConditionalBranch([1, 23, 0, 7, 0])
      CallCommonEvent([42])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 1])
      ShowText(["STOP WHERE YOU STAND, KID!"])
      ControlSelfSwitch(["A", 0])
      Empty([])

    BranchEnd([])
    Empty([])

  Page 1
    Comment([":update:"])
    ControlVariables([24, 24, 0, 3, 5, -1, 0])
    ControlVariables([25, 25, 0, 3, 5, -1, 1])
    ControlVariables([621, 621, 0, 3, 7, 0, 0])
    ConditionalBranch([6, -1, 8])
      ControlVariables([26, 26, 0, 1, 24])
      ControlVariables([27, 27, 0, 1, 25])
      ControlVariables([27, 27, 1, 0, 1])
      Wait([60])
      SetEventLocation([15, 1, 26, 27, 8])
      ShowAnimation([-1, 19, true])
      ShowTextAttributes(["Evil", 2, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["Hya-ah-ah, that was easy!"])
      FadeoutScreen([])
      TintScreen(["Tone(@red=0.0, @green=0.0, @blue=0.0, @gray=0.0)", 60, false])
      SetWeatherEffects([:none, 9, 0, false])
      ErasePicture([9])
      Wait([60])
      TransferPlayer([0, 3, 4, 5, 2, 0])
      Empty([])

    Else([])
      ConditionalBranch([6, -1, 2])
        ControlVariables([26, 26, 0, 1, 24])
        ControlVariables([27, 27, 0, 1, 25])
        ControlVariables([27, 27, 2, 0, 1])
        Wait([60])
        SetEventLocation([15, 1, 26, 27, 2])
        ShowAnimation([-1, 19, true])
        ShowTextAttributes(["Evil", 2, 0, 2])
        ShowText(["Hya-ah-ah, that was easy!"])
        FadeoutScreen([])
        TintScreen(["Tone(@red=0.0, @green=0.0, @blue=0.0, @gray=0.0)", 60, false])
        SetWeatherEffects([:none, 9, 0, false])
        ErasePicture([9])
        Wait([60])
        TransferPlayer([0, 3, 4, 5, 2, 0])
        Empty([])
      Else([])
        ConditionalBranch([6, -1, 4])
          ControlVariables([26, 26, 0, 1, 24])
          ControlVariables([27, 27, 0, 1, 25])
          ControlVariables([26, 26, 1, 0, 1])
          Wait([60])
          SetEventLocation([15, 1, 26, 27, 4])
          ShowAnimation([-1, 19, true])
          ShowTextAttributes(["Evil", 2, 0, 2])
          ShowText(["Hya-ah-ah, that was easy!"])
          FadeoutScreen([])
          TintScreen(["Tone(@red=0.0, @green=0.0, @blue=0.0, @gray=0.0)", 60, false])
          SetWeatherEffects([:none, 9, 0, false])
          ErasePicture([9])
          Wait([60])
          TransferPlayer([0, 3, 4, 5, 2, 0])
          Empty([])
        Else([])
          ConditionalBranch([6, -1, 6])
            ControlVariables([26, 26, 0, 1, 24])
            ControlVariables([27, 27, 0, 1, 25])
            ControlVariables([26, 26, 2, 0, 1])
            Wait([60])
            SetEventLocation([15, 1, 26, 27, 6])
            ShowAnimation([-1, 19, true])
            ShowTextAttributes(["Evil", 2, 0, 2])
            ShowText(["Hya-ah-ah, that was easy!"])
            FadeoutScreen([])
            TintScreen(["Tone(@red=0.0, @green=0.0, @blue=0.0, @gray=0.0)", 60, false])
            SetWeatherEffects([:none, 9, 0, false])
            ErasePicture([9])
            Wait([60])
            TransferPlayer([0, 3, 4, 5, 2, 0])
            Empty([])
          Else([])
            Empty([])
          BranchEnd([])
          Empty([])
        BranchEnd([])
        Empty([])
      BranchEnd([])
      Empty([])

    BranchEnd([])
    Empty([])

  Page 2
    Comment([":update:"])
    FadeinScreen([])
    Empty([])

  Page 3
    Comment([":update:"])
    Wait([900])
    ControlVariables([24, 24, 0, 3, 5, -1, 0])
    ControlVariables([25, 25, 0, 3, 5, -1, 1])
    ConditionalBranch([6, -1, 8])
      ControlVariables([26, 26, 0, 1, 24])
      ControlVariables([27, 27, 0, 1, 25])

CommonEvent 59
Name = "EV059"

  Page 0
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["Short Introduction to mechanics"])
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["As you see now that humans are "])
    ShowText(["at war with slimes and golems you"])
    ShowText(["can see how's the war going "])
    ShowText(["directly in the world map."])
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["More a kingdom is at advantage on"])
    ShowText(["the other, more his army will get "])
    ShowText(["close to the enemy castle."])
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["If the situation permits it an army"])
    ShowText(["can conquer a kingdom without you "])
    ShowText(["having to lift a finger."])
    ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
    ShowText(["You can help one army or the other "])
    ShowText(["in various ways:"])
    ShowChoices([["Explain Strength Points", "Explain Defense Points", "Explain Affinity Points", "Explain Wealth Points"], 5])
    When([0, "Explain Strength Points"])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["Strength Points (SP) can be gained by"])
      ShowText(["a faction winning battles, upgrading their"])
      ShowText(["army, recruiting generals (not in demo)."])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["The higher the SP difference more an "])
      ShowText(["army will be stronger than the one"])
      ShowText(["he's warring with."])
      Empty([])

    When([1, "Explain Defense Points"])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["Defense Points (DP) can be gained"])
      ShowText(["upgrading the city walls."])
      ShowText(["High DP means resisting a siege for a "])
      ShowText(["longer time without losing automatically."])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["With 0 DP an army can resist "])
      ShowText(["a siege for 2 minutes."])
      ShowText(["If you want to save that princess"])
      ShowText(["you better run for it."])
      Empty([])

    When([2, "Explain Affinity Points"])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["Affinity Points (AP) represent the bond "])
      ShowText(["you enstabilish with a faction and are "])
      ShowText(["gained helping them in battle and "])
      ShowText(["upgrading their techs."])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["High AP means you having "])
      ShowText(["the permission to visit their princess"])
      ShowText(["and influence their decision in matters"])
      ShowText(["of war."])
      Empty([])

    When([3, "Explain Wealth Points"])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["Wealth Points (WP) represent how much"])
      ShowText(["bling a faction has."])
      ShowText(["WP can be gained conquering enemy "])
      ShowText(["cities and other facilities (not in demo)."])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["Each WP adds 1SP and 1DP."])
      ShowText(["But there's more!"])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["WP increase exponentially,so it needs "])
      ShowText(["less time to go from 2WP to 3WP "])
      ShowText(["compared from 1WP to 2WP."])
      Empty([])

    WhenCancel([])
      ShowTextAttributes(["", 0, 0, 2])
      ShowText(["This ends the introduction, have fun."])
      Empty([])

    ChoicesEnd([])
    Empty([])
